xtce:Parameter.name: PCEM_RATE_ST
xtce:Parameter.xtce:LongDescription: The count rate threshold for the PCEM counter has been exceeded once and has continued to be exceeded despite measures by SWAPIFW. The PCEM count rate threshold defaults to TBD but can be updated with command TBD.

xtce:Parameter.name: SCEM_RATE_ST
xtce:Parameter.xtce:LongDescription: The count rate threshold for the SCEM counter has been exceeded once and has continued to be exceeded despite measures by SWAPIFW. The SCEM count rate threshold defaults to TBD but can be updated with command TBD.

xtce:Parameter.name: PCEM_I_ST
xtce:Parameter.xtce:LongDescription: The current threshold for the PCEM has been exceeded once and has continued to be exceeded despite measures by SWAPIFW. An overcurrent on the CEM's collectively trips an interrupt which the SWAPIFW handles. The SWAPIFW also collects the PCEM current monitor for comparison at 1 Hz. The CEM current rate threshold defaults to TBD but can be updated with command TBD.

xtce:Parameter.name: SCEM_I_ST
xtce:Parameter.xtce:LongDescription: The current threshold for the SCEM has been exceeded once and has continued to be exceeded despite measures by SWAPIFW. An overcurrent on the CEMs collectively trips an interrupt which the SWAPIFW handles. The SWAPIFW also collects the SCEM current monitor for comparison at 1 Hz. The CEM current rate threshold defaults to TBD but can be updated with command TBD.

xtce:Parameter.name: PCEM_V_ST
xtce:Parameter.xtce:LongDescription: The voltage tolerance for the PCEM for its current setting has been exceeded. The PCEM voltage tolerance is set by SWAPIFW and cannot be altered by command.

xtce:Parameter.name: SCEM_V_ST
xtce:Parameter.xtce:LongDescription: The voltage tolerance for the SCEM for its current setting has been exceeded. The SCEM voltage tolerance is set by SWAPIFW and cannot be altered by command.

xtce:Parameter.name: UND_T_ST
